title: Absolute Zero (1995) - WIN-ALL
description:
There's a new alien race on the prowl, and you've got to help the people escape before it's too late. Using a series of unique vehicles, you'll transport citizens to safety while using an array of weapons to fend off extra-terrestrial attackers. There are a total of 30 missions to keep you occupied, and three different environments in which all of the action takes place: space, land, and beneath the moon's surface. Space travel might be easy in the 24th century, but battling aliens is still difficult.

1.Extract anywhere.
2.Press "START THE GAME" batch file.
3.Play.

Compatible with WIN-ALL
